---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@/components/container.astro";
import Sectionhead from "@/components/sectionhead.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<Layout title="AI Systems" description="AnichLabs designs and builds production AI systems: AI agents, intelligent automation, and AI-powered systems deployed where the project requires, with full audit trails.">
  <Container>
    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">AI Systems</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">AI agents, intelligent automation, and AI-powered systems. Audit-ready and built to last.</Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-16">
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">
        Most AI products solve the wrong problem, or solve the right problem
        wrong. Engineering teams have the skills to build sophisticated AI
        systems, but without domain understanding embedded in requirements,
        products miss the workflow, ignore the regulatory shape of the use
        case, or generate outputs that nobody trusts. The pattern repeats
        across healthcare, finance, legal, and any sector where decisions
        carry weight.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg mt-4">
        AnichLabs OÜ designs and builds AI systems that operate under
        real-world constraints. Our work spans AI agents for operational
        workflows, intelligent automation pipelines, and AI-powered systems,
        running on infrastructure chosen for the project, with full audit
        trails. AnichLabs translates domain needs into technically sound and reliable
        AI products.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">What we deliver</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:robot" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">AI Agents and Automation</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Event-driven systems with role-routed prompts, RAG, and human oversight, built for the workflows your team actually runs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:notes" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">AI Strategy</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Use case definition, product requirements, and regulatory alignment, before you build.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:server" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Sovereign Deployment</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">EU hosting, on-premise, or edge - deployed where the project requires. CPU-only or GPU. No US providers when the client needs that boundary.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:user-md" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Clinical and Domain Advisory</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Available throughout development to review outputs, advise on validation, and support regulatory submissions when required.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Common questions</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-5 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sm">
            How is this different from a generic AI agency?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-3">Generic agencies wire up prompts and APIs. We design AI systems with audit trails, role-based access, sovereign deployment options, and the workflow understanding to know when an AI output should never reach a user without review. The architecture and the discipline are the difference.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-5 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sm">
            At what stage should we engage?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-3">As early as possible. Domain and architectural decisions made before the first line of code save months of rework later. We also work with teams reviewing or rebuilding existing products.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-5 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sm">
            Can this be combined with regulatory compliance work?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-3">Yes. AI systems and EU AI Act compliance are tightly linked. We often deliver them as a combined engagement so your product is technically and regulatorily aligned from day one.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl mt-16 mb-10 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">Building intelligent systems that need to work?</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mt-3">Book a free 30-minute call to discuss your project.</p>
      <a href="https://calendly.com/chris-anichlabs/30min" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
        class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors"
        style="background-color: #003399">
        <Icon name="uil:calendar-alt" class="w-5 h-5" />
        Book a Free Call
      </a>
    </div>

  </Container>
</Layout>
